ft og d\u00f8d til en oppl\u00f8ftende og overraskende livsbejaende film."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "kultur|film"}, {"field": "category2", "value": "kultur|film|filmanmeldelser"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "1691111cbbff9410b215d8e20d1251a7b38f957cefe0a70766569fa4f1e788d6"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-02-12T16:39:11.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Varmt og overraskende oppl\u00f8ftende om 23-\u00e5rig tobarnsmor som f\u00e5r kreft og n\u00e5del\u00f8s d\u00f8dsdom."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1078831.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ver2%20mittlilvBig"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/e728ec9b14febe5e7e2d54a02b58f382c3ce91de.jpg?591ee7fb"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Livsbejaende om d\u00f8den -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "e728ec9b14febe5e7e2d54a02b58f382c3ce91de"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": "Movie"}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Movie"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["kultur", "filmanmeldelser", "film"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "arts-and-entertainment"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["d\u00f8d", "livsbejaende", "film"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["dying young", "ann"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "norge"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["isabel coixet", "julia roberts", "sarah polley", "pedro almodovar"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["kultur/film/filmanmeldelser", "kultur", "kultur/film"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1078831.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ver2%20mittlilvBig"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field": "og-title", "va